33. Mahayana Mind Training
472 
[194] To Maitreya, Asariga, and so on; 
To Serlingpa and to master Atisa; 
To Dromtonpa, Potowa, and Sharawa; 
And to Maldro473 and Drakmarwa,474 I pay homage. 
